<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="address-vt">address <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'dres/    美 /ə'dres/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在…上写姓名、地址：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please address the letter for me. 
请替我在信上写地址。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That letter was <strong>addressed to</strong> me.
那封信是寄给我的。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>对...演说 / 演讲；[正式用语] 对...说话：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>address</strong> <strong>a</strong> <strong>meeting</strong> 
在会议上发表演讲</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was surprised when he addressed me in fluent English.
他用流利的英语和我说话时我很惊讶。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>称呼：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Swiss tend to be formal and address each other by last name.
瑞士人往往比较庄重，相互之间用姓氏称呼彼此。</p><footer>2014 浙江</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>[正式用语] 设法解决；处理</strong></h4>
<p>to try to deal with a problem：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>address a problem / question</strong>
处理问题</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Fill in the form with your name, home a<strong><em>_</em></strong>_____, and phone number.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. address  </p></div>